OL,3,CSenedd recalled during summer break to
OL,4,Cchoose new First Minister
OL,6,FThe Welsh Parliament has been recalled
OL,7,Fduring its summer break to nominate a
OL,8,Fnew First Minister of Wales.
OL,10,FIt comes after Vaughan Gething
OL,11,Fresigned as First Minister and leader
OL,12,Fof the Welsh Labour party last week.
OL,14,FEluned Morgan has since been confirmed
OL,15,Fas the new leader of Welsh Labour and
OL,16,Fthe likely first minister of Wales.
