OL,3,CSenedd recalled during summer break to
OL,4,Cchoose new First Minister
OL,6,FHowever, a vote in the Senedd is
OL,7,Frequired before she can become first
OL,8,Fminister. The Welsh parliament was due
OL,9,Fto be on recess until September, but
OL,10,Fthe Senedd will now meet on Tuesday, 6
OL,11,FAugust at 11am.
OL,13,FThe Llywydd of the Senedd Elin Jones
OL,14,FMS, the Presiding Officer, says: "I
OL,15,Freceived a request from the First
OL,16,FMinister to recall the Senedd for
OL,17,FMembers to nominate the next person to
OL,18,Ftake on the role of First Minister of
OL,19,FWales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
