OL,4,Cchoose new First Minister
OL,6,F"I have agreed to the request and I
OL,7,Fhave written to Members of the Senedd
OL,8,Fto inform them of the recall."
OL,10,FThe Senedd can be recalled during
OL,11,Frecess, on the authority of the
OL,12,FLlywydd, to discuss issues of national
OL,13,Fsignificance.
OL,15,FIn its 25-year history, it has
OL,16,Fpreviously been recalled to discuss
OL,17,Fthe response to the Covid-19 Pandemic,
OL,18,FBrexit and the future of the steel
OL,19,Findustry.
