OL,3,CSenedd recalled during summer break to
OL,4,Cchoose new First Minister
OL,6,FHowever, this is the first time it
OL,7,Fwill meet in recess to nominate a new
OL,8,FFirst Minister.
OL,10,FThe meeting will be hybrid, with some
OL,11,FMembers present in the debating
OL,12,Fchamber - the Siambr - with the option
OL,13,Fto also participate virtually.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Mr Gething said: "I
OL,16,Fhave today written to the Llywydd
OL,17,F(Presiding Officer), in accordance
OL,18,Fwith Standing Order 12.3, to request
OL,19,Farrangements are made to recall the
OL,20,FSenedd on 6 August to nominate a new
OL,21,Ffirst minister.
