OL,6,F"This is subject to receiving His
OL,7,FMajesty the King's acceptance of my
OL,8,Fformal offer of resignation."
OL,10,FAndrew RT Davies MS, Leader of the
OL,11,FWelsh Conservatives welcomed the
OL,12,Frecall, saying: "I am grateful to the
OL,13,FFirst Minister for heeding Welsh
OL,14,FConservative calls to recall the
OL,15,FSenedd to give Wales some much-needed
OL,16,Fstability.
