OL,6,F"Considering the chaos that has
OL,7,Fengulfed the Labour Government in
OL,8,FCardiff Bay you would have thought
OL,9,Fthey would have brought this decision
OL,10,Fforward by bringing in an earlier
OL,11,Frecall to give Wales that stability.
OL,13,F"Given that Eluned Morgan's delivery
OL,14,Fas Health Minister was questionable,
OL,15,Fyou would have also thought that she
OL,16,Fwould want to get going straight away
OL,17,Fby being elected by the Senedd as
OL,18,FFirst Minister."
