OL,3,CSenedd recalled during summer break to
OL,4,Cchoose new First Minister
OL,6,FThe First Minister will need to
OL,7,Fofficially submit his resignation to
OL,8,Fthe King ahead of the meeting.
OL,10,FOnce the King has accepted, the
OL,11,FLlywydd will notify the Senedd. The
OL,12,Fnomination of a new First Minister can
OL,13,Fnow take place in the meeting on
OL,14,FAugust 6.
OL,16,FDuring the meeting, the Llywydd will
OL,17,Fask for nominations for First Minister
OL,18,Ffrom Members of the Senedd. Any Member
OL,19,Fof the Senedd can nominate any other
OL,20,FMember to be First Minister.
