OL,3,CSenedd recalled during summer break to
OL,4,Cchoose new First Minister
OL,6,FIf one Member is put forward, that
OL,7,Fperson becomes the 'nominee.' If more
OL,8,Fthan one Member is put forward, all
OL,9,Fthe Members of Senedd vote via roll
OL,10,Fcall, except for the Llywydd and
OL,11,FDeputy Presiding Officer.
OL,13,FMembers will be called one by one to
OL,14,Fdeclare which Member they support.
OL,16,FOnce the Senedd has chosen a new First
OL,17,FMinister, the Llywydd will write to
OL,18,Fthe King recommending the 'nominee' to
OL,19,Fbecome First Minister.
